Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:27.42,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:30.15,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:40.61,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,You little turd! You think I can't reach you up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.12,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How long are you gonna keep picking on him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:51.45,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for the prey to be killed by the predator.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:52.20,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:53.27,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:57.90,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,But he's toying with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.90,0:01:00.93,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Quit arguing and give me a hand here, you heartless jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:04.13,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let you use me as a stepping stool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:05.41,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:12.34,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I TOLD you, you could stand on top of my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:14.04,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,Hi guys! Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:16.39,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,You can use my back if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:21.00,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pretty generous guy. Unlike this grouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:22.94,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Rygart. Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.34,0:01:24.08,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Hodr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.30,0:01:25.90,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Hodr.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:27.34,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then. I'll take my shoes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:30.26,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:33.29,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to give this uniform a much-needed washing anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.29,0:01:36.32,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Would you rather I piggybacked instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:40.19,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,Nah. That would be rather awkward for both of us, so no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:45.27,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:45.87,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:49.16,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.48,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's a baby Black Owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:59.45,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,He'll slowly start turning black.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.52,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know your birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:02.41,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:03.80,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:08.45,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,The man you just stepped on is the heir to the throne of your nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.28,0:02:12.24,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,What did he just...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:17.15,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your Majesty, I offer you this bird and beg for your forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.51,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable. You don't even know your own King's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.51,0:02:21.85,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.86,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Zess! You know the conditions for surrender, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:49.51,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,The conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.10,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,There are two conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:55.02,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Both of which involve the vested privileges of the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:59.01,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Hodr is a generous king.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:04.90,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,He even risked causing conflict among the nobles over allowing ordinary citizens to hold office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.56,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,The terms should be more than reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.28,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something else to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.77,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you get involved, Rygart?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:19.30,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,He should be well aware of our military's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:22.34,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you just surrender, Hodr?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:54.04,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from our remaining ammunition stores, \Nwe can afford to fight one more battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.64,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we proceed as planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:06:01.37,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We'll make a third strike on \NBinonten, then retreat to the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.30,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.48,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.38,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.36,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:19.21,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,During the Krisnan war of independence,\N they slaughtered civilians near the borders,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.79,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,hacked off the limbs of our captured soldiers, and sent them to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:27.21,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Now they're building favor with Orlando, and \Nthreatening this continent's peace once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:30.22,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,They are savage, despicable people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:32.17,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight them until I draw my last breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:41.29,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Lee told me not to bring my emotions into \Nbattle, but I WILL bring down the Black Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:46.17,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over night watch duties. Please rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.10,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I said I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.43,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,I never said anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.92,0:06:59.73,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,History lessons sure have changed from when I was in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:02.75,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,I was taught the same things as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:06.31,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,History books are rewritten with the changing of the times, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:12.07,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, classroom lectures are worlds apart from the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.57,Default,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,Quit dragging your asses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.99,Default,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for their ladder sweepers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:56.21,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,But General, attacking them would mean sacrificing our own forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:58.28,Default,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,Then think of another way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.28,0:07:59.56,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,General Hoeckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:07:59.90,Default,Hoe,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:03.75,Default,Hoe,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.20,Default,Hoe,0000,0000,0000,,He's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:13.62,Default,Hoe,0000,0000,0000,,Borcuse... is on the move...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.27,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Pay attention, Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:25.17,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,This multi-layer armor was made from \Nleftover medium-strength armor plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:30.39,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,While it's equipped, the Delphine's combat \Ncapabilities are reduced by 80 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:33.08,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,By gripping the lever tightly, you can disengage the armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:34.62,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch your timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.81,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Also, about that strange display.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.26,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:43.41,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,When the red bar reaches the end, you'll be rendered immobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:46.67,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,And it requires approximately 24 hours to recover functionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.88,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,The operational time limit for strenuous use is roughly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:55.43,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.41,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.20,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,How much time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:00.37,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Between ten and thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.05,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really believe you have the capacity to kill though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.86,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I've already killed two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.60,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.28,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if you yourself took their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:17.54,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:24.79,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I wanted the enemy to die from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:30.11,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Or else I'd wind up dead instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.29,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,What if you were fighting Zess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:34.83,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:37.54,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Could you fight him with that same mentality?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:41.22,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Zess... There's no way I could beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.76,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a single man capable of beating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.29,Default,Cheers,0000,0000,0000,,Zess! Zess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:56.60,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,The drill instructors would wail on students \Nin mock battles to blow off steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:10:00.12,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,But even a team of four instructors couldn't defeat Zess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.11,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:22.19,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,One of our scouts has informed us of the enemy's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:24.28,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,We're commencing the operation. Are you ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.09,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,All set.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.75,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Let me say this for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:32.11,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,It is far more difficult to capture an enemy than it is to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:36.78,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Capturing a soldier involves three times \Nthe effort and three times the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:40.09,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to save the life of an enemy soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.46,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,remember that you'll lose three of your own in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.14,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:10.03,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Delphine, commence operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.40,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:15.05,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay out of General Baldr's way, Un-sorcerer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.65,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Sigyn, please stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.67,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up the pace, Cleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:42.30,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.75,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Stealth isn't necessary from this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.15,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about leaving footprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:49.60,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Affirmative!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:51.05,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.84,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Captain Zess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:56.27,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been sweeping twice to hide your steps so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:11:57.32,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:01.30,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Southern Krisna's soil is softer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.74,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to sweep at least three times?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.59,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,We're trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:31.68,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by enemy forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:34.37,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Abort mission! We're retreating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.05,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,There's an opening at 7 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.61,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Erekt! Secure our escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.28,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.97,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't necessarily your fault, Cleo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:43.37,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:45.19,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Argath and I will guard the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.11,Default,Arg/Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:47.94,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Cleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:48.81,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:55.87,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,General Baldr, the enemy's retreating!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.18,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,They figured it out already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:00.75,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier than I anticipated. \N Regardless, all units commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:19.25,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.49,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy some time! Go help Cleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.83,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Two kills already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.17,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,The Killer Golem is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:48.97,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Are you saying our ambush forces aren't worth your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.36,Default,Arg,0000,0000,0000,,You're too focused on Captain Zess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:01.91,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Can you move, Cleo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:02.90,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.67,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,They're closing in on us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:05.82,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:17.70,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we managed to break free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.58,Default,Arg,0000,0000,0000,,Badlands...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:21.35,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,We'll regroup at point nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:22.20,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.42,Default,Arg,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell IS that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.45,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Two... three... four... enemy units.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:10.66,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,How should I handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.05,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to save the life of an enemy soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:21.45,Default,Arg,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Zess, let me defend the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:24.53,Default,Arg,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.32,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back, Argath! Do not engage him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.49,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get yourself killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:53.75,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead... He's dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:54.97,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.99,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you're here means \N you feel somewhat responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.61,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Me, responsible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.65,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I don't blame myself one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.10,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I never even saw Dan's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:09.11,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.85,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, please retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:35.64,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,I'll break through that armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.90,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo, give him cover fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:38.22,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.20,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, Cleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.17,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.78,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a fortress is charging right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.45,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,This guy hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.24,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Zess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:06.38,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, he's concentrating his fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.40,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to tear off my armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:12.84,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,It can't take much more!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:15.63,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:31.40,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,What ridiculous height!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.19,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Zess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:39.70,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.65,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Get back, Erekt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.78,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,He moves so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:58.97,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:00.86,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Erekt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:03.81,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's him alright. The Black Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.06,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Golem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:06.43,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Zess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.77,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:14.22,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,If I destroy his rifle, I can save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:31.04,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:35.01,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get away from the Captain, \N I'll turn you into a beehive, Black Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.55,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,How could I have done something so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:40.34,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I held back because I was fighting Zess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:44.68,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't do something, they'll waste me the second I land!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:49.54,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,If Rygart gets too far away, Erekt and Cleo will kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.74,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be the one to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:18.26,Default,Zes,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:51.54,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Zess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.04,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Zess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.46,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,ZESS!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:07.61,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy reinforcements...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:11.27,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo, this is your final order!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.45,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,You're to retreat to the border alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:17.20,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,That's an order from your superior, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.19,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Get going, Cleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:21.55,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.86,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's been killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:28.44,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Lee, Argath, everyone from Irios...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:31.30,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,They've all died at the hands of the Black Golem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:33.92,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo, are you listening? I said retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.63,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:38.64,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.61,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:28.80,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Two hostiles sighted! Two units down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.01,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,One is the Delphine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.85,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your fire! Make sure you don't hit Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:36.69,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Erekt, I'll draw their attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:39.85,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Take the opportunity to get Captain Zess out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:42.27,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do something so delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:43.30,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:47.11,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it could go that \N smoothly in this kind of situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.66,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, what's gonna happen to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.85,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,You damn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:22.55,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Target sighted! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:27.03,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,A pressure gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.03,0:22:28.57,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Left side, don't break formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:07.60,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,T-This guy's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:22.00,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:26.06,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,I have to remove the armor carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:27.84,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,or else the Captain will get crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:43.54,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,He's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:07.13,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,General, please get back--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.60,0:24:21.69,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're all panicking over a single unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.56,0:24:34.20,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.90,0:24:36.03,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Erekt!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.45,0:24:39.79,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,I've recovered the Captain! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.79,0:24:40.45,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.66,0:24:43.10,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Let us handle this, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.10,0:24:44.04,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.59,0:24:50.92,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Chase them down! Don't just rely on your guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.92,0:24:53.34,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Fly, Artemis!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.15,0:24:58.06,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! This thing's range is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.06,0:24:59.01,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Keep firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.35,0:25:03.35,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, Cleo! Put some distance between them!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.35,0:25:06.15,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,General Baldr, it's almost out of range!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.46,0:25:12.36,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,You damned fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.36,0:25:14.20,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Erekt!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.91,0:25:21.85,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.50,0:25:27.03,Default,whatshername,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.03,0:25:29.41,Default,Whn,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate General True's troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.41,0:25:31.34,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Another unit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.68,0:25:37.09,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Erekt...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.69,0:25:39.14,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Go on without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.00,0:25:43.43,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Please... save Captain Zess.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.44,0:25:47.55,Default,Ere,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Cleo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.26,0:26:01.43,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit captured! The other has escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.49,0:26:47.79,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Zess?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.37,0:26:51.98,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately for you at least, he made a dashing retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.50,0:26:53.47,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.99,0:26:56.38,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.79,0:27:01.27,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the National Defense Force \Nis fighting off Athens' main forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.27,0:27:05.14,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,And even if they can repel them, General Borcuse is on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.83,0:27:07.99,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.23,0:27:12.78,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,It's only just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.47,0:27:17.00,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.39,0:27:43.65,Default,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, start walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.82,0:28:09.39,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How was I, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.39,0:28:11.30,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,You were wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.30,0:28:14.91,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to next month's All-Federation String Recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.91,0:28:16.29,Default,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.88,0:28:18.46,Default,Mai,0000,0000,0000,,You have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.24,0:28:26.72,Default,Gir,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. It's the Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.81,0:28:37.95,Default,Gir,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.51,0:28:40.49,Default,Col,0000,0000,0000,,Very much. It's quite delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.75,0:28:43.73,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Like he could've said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.73,0:28:44.75,Default,Gir,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.28,0:28:49.98,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, I hear you've been frequenting \Nthe mess hall these days, Colonel Ios.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.98,0:28:52.46,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of some lady friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.98,0:28:55.18,Default,Gir,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.18,0:28:56.81,Default,Col,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.81,0:28:59.62,Default,Col,0000,0000,0000,,I just enjoy being able to talk with my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.58,0:29:05.28,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.57,0:29:09.68,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.13,0:29:13.66,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,So the situation on the front lines is grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.66,0:29:18.79,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,If Krisna manages to ally with Orlando, \Nthey'll become our biggest threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.59,0:29:21.85,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,I sympathize with Secretary General Loquis.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.20,0:29:26.09,Default,Col,0000,0000,0000,,Secretary General Loquis has sought your \Nreinstatement more fervently than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.09,0:29:30.03,Default,Col,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, he's aware of your heroic \Ndeeds during the siege of Assam Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.85,0:29:35.65,Default,Col,0000,0000,0000,,He also testified to your innocence \Nduring your Federal Court Marshall.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.94,0:29:41.90,Default,Col,0000,0000,0000,,And at the same time, he has transferred full \Ncommand of the Krisnan subjugation forces to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.65,0:29:45.30,Default,Col,0000,0000,0000,,...General Borcuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.22,0:29:48.52,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.52,0:29:49.99,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,I will topple Krisna.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.53,0:29:54.68,Default,Gir,0000,0000,0000,,Father, Colonel...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.92,0:29:57.09,Default,Gir,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving for the battlefield again, aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.09,0:29:59.37,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Sorrow's just part of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.37,0:30:01.90,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return unharmed like I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.90,0:30:04.11,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,So don't you worry, Leda.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.02,0:30:08.35,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there for your recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.35,0:30:10.54,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the Colonel, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.25,0:30:14.87,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.45,0:30:15.97,Default,Col,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.15,0:30:32.54,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel, how's my Hycherion?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.54,0:30:37.49,Default,Col,0000,0000,0000,,We figured out a way to transport it and \Nsent it to Irios for further repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.49,0:30:38.52,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,And my men?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.12,0:30:41.19,Default,Col,0000,0000,0000,,They're assembling in Irios.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.19,0:30:42.24,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.28,0:31:12.30,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.51,0:31:13.59,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you don't need to rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.28,0:31:14.74,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.51,0:31:19.94,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I just have a killer headache, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.65,0:31:26.94,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Black Golem's pilot...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.94,0:31:29.57,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,The one who injured Captain Zess, and killed Lee and Argath.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.57,0:31:34.91,Default,Lee,0000,0000,0000,,You filthy savages!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.00,0:31:38.58,Default,Lee,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die than be humiliated!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.98,0:31:44.38,Default,Lee,0000,0000,0000,,You barbarians!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.30,0:31:52.05,Default,BAl,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy Knight 1st Class Narvi, you played \Na major part in the prisoner's capture.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.05,0:31:53.36,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear your thoughts on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.50,0:32:00.61,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect, General Baldr, our squad contributed absolutely nothing to the capture.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.61,0:32:06.79,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,To take credit for doing so would be to \Ndisgrace the reputation of this nation's Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.79,0:32:11.32,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, I feel that I am not qualified \Nto participate in this discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.15,0:32:13.94,Default,Tru,0000,0000,0000,,Well said, Narvi!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.94,0:32:15.99,Default,Tru,0000,0000,0000,,Spoken like a true knight of this kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.45,0:32:19.72,Default,Tru,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we shall excuse \N ourselves from this meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.72,0:32:21.21,Default,Tru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Narvi!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.21,0:32:22.13,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.64,0:32:32.22,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Getting information out of the \N prisoner is of the utmost importance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.22,0:32:36.20,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,However, at the same time, we must exercise \Nextreme caution when dealing with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.61,0:32:41.56,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart, your input is very important as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.10,0:32:44.10,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.10,0:32:45.05,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.05,0:32:46.44,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do with our prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.05,0:32:48.94,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Why not just release her to Athens?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.59,0:32:50.46,Default,Bal,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.43,0:32:52.98,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.18,0:32:58.50,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,There's a chance she may commit suicide. \NWould you please let me handle this matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.19,0:33:02.37,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,She may prove useful in refitting the new Golem.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.98,0:33:04.79,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Please, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.68,0:33:24.27,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,So you want me to master this thing in a week, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.27,0:33:32.70,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you say? The only person capable of \Npiloting it besides yourself would be Lady Narvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.39,0:33:36.76,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of these shackles and I'll pilot whatever you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.76,0:33:38.62,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It sure feels nice to be relied upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.88,0:33:43.37,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,A new squad centered around the Delphine is being formed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.37,0:33:47.54,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,It's been suggested that you enter \N under the command of their captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.96,0:33:55.05,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I might lose my temper and \N accidentally shoot my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.70,0:33:56.88,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.36,0:34:08.83,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what they do to me, I won't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.83,0:34:12.45,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes down to it, I'll just smash \Nmy head into the walls until I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.29,0:34:25.96,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.18,0:34:34.00,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,This is the torture chamber?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.64,0:34:36.25,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,These are my private quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.25,0:34:39.30,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little messy, but please bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.30,0:34:40.43,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,A little?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.70,0:34:45.45,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I am the wife of Krisna's king, Sigyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.45,0:34:46.35,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.72,0:34:47.70,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.46,0:34:51.02,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I told her my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.80,0:34:56.20,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,The king's wife... That makes her the queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.71,0:34:58.11,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo Saubraffe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.12,0:35:01.74,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,This is the crest of the famous House Saubraffe, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.74,0:35:05.41,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't find anything suspicious, so \NI was permitted to return it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.55,0:35:14.59,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that you treasure it dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.32,0:35:22.36,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,She's so beautiful... and gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.91,0:35:25.93,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all like a barbarian princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.93,0:35:29.16,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still an enemy soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.16,0:35:31.26,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be fooled so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.26,0:35:33.00,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pour us some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.42,0:35:37.19,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're up to, \Nbut I'm not going to tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.19,0:35:40.67,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo, you're welcome to stay here in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.67,0:35:44.00,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I cannot allow you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.49,0:35:51.95,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I would also like to have a private discussion \Nregarding things like Zess and your new golems.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.95,0:35:57.37,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to treat you as a guest as long as you stay \Nhere. You'll be fine even if you don't wish to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.26,0:36:01.55,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,You're being quite soft on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.25,0:36:05.60,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,The Krisnan forces are not \N used to dealing with prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.11,0:36:10.71,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I'll begin the questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.35,0:36:15.15,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,You singlehandedly brought down an estimated five golems.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.62,0:36:18.70,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Yet miraculously, none of the pilots were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.60,0:36:23.20,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Did you purposely avoid killing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.51,0:36:27.11,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,If such sophisticated maneuvers are \Npossible with a golem as complex as yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.66,0:36:30.32,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,then you must be an extremely capable sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.71,0:36:39.65,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder... Does that make you a model soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.76,0:36:43.09,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.57,0:36:57.97,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.97,0:37:00.30,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,She's an adult, yet she's so frail...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.30,0:37:02.40,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there's someone weaker than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.07,0:37:08.03,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.46,0:37:14.90,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,You've shown me great kindness, but unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.90,0:37:16.10,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.15,0:37:23.64,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Remove your garments too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.70,0:37:26.97,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to disrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.39,0:37:31.77,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.77,0:37:32.82,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.82,0:37:35.23,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem? Just eat your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.81,0:37:41.55,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I see your proud animal spirit hasn't been completely broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.67,0:37:46.53,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where ya goin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.26,0:37:49.73,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come back when he gets tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.69,0:37:52.75,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,You mean when he gets hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.76,0:38:02.67,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,Rygart.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.67,0:38:03.80,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.30,0:38:07.24,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,That prisoner girl... Apparently she's only 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.76,0:38:09.05,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,12 years old?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.54,0:38:10.97,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,Well...yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.37,0:38:13.62,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that body of hers?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.72,0:38:18.30,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Is she seriously 12 years old? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.30,0:38:19.30,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.90,0:38:22.25,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,What did Athens do to her body?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.89,0:38:34.82,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.82,0:38:35.62,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.62,0:38:38.17,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped Gram's food.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.17,0:38:39.55,Default,Hod,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.26,0:38:41.26,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.82,0:38:53.35,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Call the guards inside without making a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.30,0:39:02.91,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think you can \N escape to the border by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.91,0:39:04.12,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.90,0:39:25.75,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Black Golem's pilot...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.95,0:39:29.97,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Cleo...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.95,0:39:37.02,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Hey man, what're you tryin' to pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.02,0:39:39.46,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,You're a little heavy, you stupid bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.09,0:39:42.77,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,How about you GET THE HELL OFF?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.79,0:39:48.02,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,What's your deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.02,0:39:50.85,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Try that again and I'll break your damn wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.07,0:40:04.47,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,You've really put on weight, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.47,0:40:06.88,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I guess "grown" would be a nicer way to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.45,0:40:10.06,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when you were a little squirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.06,0:40:15.14,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a birdbrain like you probably can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.14,0:40:17.08,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,I used to take care of you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.26,0:40:20.33,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,So did Zess.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.75,0:40:25.07,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Old Captain Serious, Zess, used to help out a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.34,0:40:31.26,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,At first, he was so clumsy that he nearly dropped his poker face.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.26,0:40:34.91,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,But he was the first who offered to care for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.10,0:40:40.27,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still remember him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.27,0:40:44.58,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,He used to show off and let you perch on his shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.23,0:40:47.21,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I nearly cracked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.21,0:40:50.51,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, everyone was too scared to actually laugh at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.60,0:40:55.00,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause there was nobody tough enough to beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.89,0:41:02.64,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Zess can't possibly lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.41,0:41:10.03,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... if he had taken you home with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.90,0:41:14.79,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Agh, why am I spilling my guts to a dumb bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.70,0:41:17.39,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Zess...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.19,0:41:32.59,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.98,0:41:33.80,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.01,0:41:35.64,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any rounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.92,0:41:38.94,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.37,0:41:41.93,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Cleo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.10,0:41:47.77,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terrified of guns. I can't even shoot one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.84,0:41:59.01,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange that I was able to take your gun so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.61,0:42:01.76,Default,Cle,0000,0000,0000,,You went easy on me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.76,0:42:02.65,Default,Gua,0000,0000,0000,,Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.21,0:42:14.92,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,OW! You little--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.53,0:42:23.14,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I did try to fight you off, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.03,0:42:27.76,Default,Ryg,0000,0000,0000,,Your claws are digging into me, you little bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.86,0:45:32.62,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,110... 111!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.05,0:45:35.55,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they just keep coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.40,0:45:49.20,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,To our people, we're on a mission to punish the \Npuny, conniving nation that's hiding behind Orlando.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.17,0:45:52.31,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Is that truly how other nations see us, General?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.69,0:45:56.00,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Are you having some personal doubts about this conflict, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.30,0:46:00.99,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,If you consider international affairs as personal, then yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.94,0:46:08.67,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't made this public, but our \Nquartz mines are beginning to run dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.67,0:46:11.15,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Even counting our emergency reserves, \Nwe've probably got another ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.15,0:46:15.28,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to find more abundant lands no matter what the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.95,0:46:21.56,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only option we have left...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.45,0:46:27.59,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,At the risk of sounding arrogant, I support the invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.05,0:46:33.95,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Since their country's defeat at Assam, Orlando's \Npacifist faction has gained significant influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.95,0:46:36.52,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, I highly doubt they'll get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.14,0:46:41.94,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of opportunity comes only once every 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.23,0:46:48.54,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you, the man willing to play the villain \Nfor his country's sake, more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.30,0:46:55.12,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Athens' future is in your hands, General Borcuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.10,0:47:02.72,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,Fight for your friends, your family, \Nand the very peace of this continent!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.08,0:47:05.09,Default,Bor,0000,0000,0000,,All forces, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.37,0:47:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will crush Baldr.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.89,0:47:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then this war will be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.52,0:47:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No big deal. He's already dead anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.98,0:47:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think of it as demolition work.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.77,0:47:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.77,0:47:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to become a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.66,0:47:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he acts the least bit suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.41,0:47:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kill him without hesitation!
